{"tid":1740423,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我話埋畀你知呢場運動一撚定失敗","createTime":"2019-11-20T02:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T02:44:38.000Z","uid":258069,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1d2a19b31bb0a71c1cc0d69e2b862f68751f42","tid":1740423,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:29:34.000Z","msg":"一隊6人前線小隊宣布退出運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n代po<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌哂你班撚樣，一見到唔啱睇就講乜撚嘢失敗主義，拉。<br />\n啱呀，做人唔撚好檢討最撚好，一世活喺平行世界。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我外國讀書，為咗Poly 班手足，洗哂全部積蓄返嚟香港，<br />\n我返到去飯都冇得食，而家喺香港都係朋友接滯。<br />\n然後呢？入撚到去就成班喺度開Party，<br />\n<br />\n人哋隔籬做嘢緊就有件八婆喺度講是非，數手足不是，<br />\n驚死人哋唔知佢發夢。<br />\n<br />\n之後有個戇鳩婆喺兩個火魔工廠之間用火魔，<br />\n用完畀人屌，佢就搞辯話：點知入面入咗氣油，係尋晚班手足整㗎。<br />\n屌你老母臭閪，小學生都知唔撚好喺易燃物附近點火，何況係火魔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁既然開Party 開得咁開心，我返屋企瞓覺好過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未畀曱甴打已經畀你班智將tk 咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返撚到外國，發現Poly 畀人打緊，外面有班人幫你引開啲狗，<br />\n你班蛋散就投降自首，飲水都捱到一星期，<br />\n何況入面有人煮，有一定糧食，除咗重傷我睇唔到點解要投降。<br />\n係投降嘅，其實唔使叫我哋出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n人哋熊仔頭幫手足走，<br />\n某個將軍澳地區Channel 喺度將熊仔頭條Message 放出嚟 <br />\n文盲定鬼，叫你用圈子「一個一個」咁轉發，<br />\n文盲唔好做Channel啦 屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都未屌幾個月前嘅嘢，過咗咁而可以算。<br />\n我淨係知咁耐以嚟都係失望同失望 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開花搞到冇工返，唔割；<br />\n我全家人冇工返，唔割；<br />\n勇武差啲畀人搞到人踩人，唔割；<br />\n然後返返嚟做勇武，失望。<br />\n<br />\n要拉拉飽佢，一班手足喺前線後台不眠不休幫你哋，<br />\n你哋諗下自己做緊乜嘢？<br />\n<br />\n我身家得返500 蚊，<br />\n但我重有5000 蚊機票要找數，<br />\n我返外國開開心心做港豬唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講返，我不接受任何捐輸。一蚊都唔撚要。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9ed95ea6c56e4d37f2cfb1d86008a92115710041","tid":1740423,"uid":34942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住手足<br />\n唔好放棄呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb52c708a38ac487eb99442e65b5a64e76e78348","tid":1740423,"uid":256505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:44:21.000Z","msg":"和理非唔知點抗爭？唔想放棄？<br />\n唔想做失敗撚？ 入黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［進擊的和理非］<br />\n和理非武裝化 - 知識篇 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/eyJDKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/eyJDKT</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4d4e90d23f2046e803734142861a63d00dc8c496","tid":1740423,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed95ea6c56e4d37f2cfb1d86008a92115710041","tid":1740423,"uid":34942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住手足<br />\n唔好放棄呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:44:38.000Z","msg":"我問過白己，<br />\n如果喺隔籬瞓緊嘅我畀嗰個智將手足燒撚到<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母，我唔割，燒到最多未返外國睇個醫生，畀人笑下。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我想你哋生性啲，長進啲 <br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打仗呀 大佬 改變心態呀要</span></strong></span>"}]}